Author: Yerzmyey/AY-RIDERS
Album: Brutal & Aggressive
Total time: 20:19 min.

Cover:
This short compilation contains chiptune/micromusic stuff in heavy and brutal style of Electro-industrial/Breakbeat/tek with typical YM/AY acid synthetic sounds.

Composed on ZX Spectrum 48K with AY-interface.
Recorded using ZX Spectrum 48K with AY-interface and ATARI 520ST.
